Package: mcgf
Title: Simulate (Regime-Switching) Markov Chain Gaussian Field Over a Lattice
Version: 0.0.0.1000
Authors@R: 
    person("Tianxia", "Jia", , "tianxia.jia@ucalgary.ca", 
    role = c("aut", "cre"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5430-5019"))
Description: A package to simulate samples for Markov chain Gaussian fields 
    with covariance functions of the Gneiting class by simple kriging. User 
    defined covariance functions are supported. Simple kriging is used for 
    simulation.
